org.hornetq.jms.client

Class HornetQMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hornetq.jms.client.HornetQMessage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javax.jms.Message
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    HornetQBytesMessage, HornetQMapMessage, HornetQObjectMessage, HornetQStreamMessage, HornetQTextMessage

    public class HornetQMessage
extends Object
implements javax.jms.Message
    HornetQ implementation of a JMS Message.
    JMS Messages only live on the client side - the server only deals with MessageImpl instances
    Author:
    Ovidiu Feodorov, Tim Fox, Tyronne Wickramarathne Partially ported from JBossMQ implementation originally written by:, Norbert Lataille (Norbert.Lataille@m4x.org), Hiram Chirino (Cojonudo14@hotmail.com), David Maplesden (David.Maplesden@orion.co.nz), Adrian Brock, Andy Taylor, Clebert Suconic
